[03:25.53]	Yon knight doth sit too melancholy,
[03:28.88]	As if the entertainment in our court
[03:32.41]	Had not a show might countervail his worth.
[03:36.42]	Note it not you, Thaisa?
[03:38.79]THAISA	What is it
[03:40.18]	To me, my father?
[03:41.99]SIMONIDES	O, attend, my daughter:
[03:44.20]	Princes in this should live like gods above,
[03:48.29]	Who freely give to every one that comes
[03:52.06]	To honour them:
[03:53.78]	And princes not doing so are like to gnats,
[03:57.79]	Which make a sound, but kill'd are wonder'd at.
