[04:47.74]THAISA	Wishing it so much blood unto your life.
[04:51.51]PERICLES	I thank both him and you, and pledge him freely.
[04:55.85]THAISA	And further he desires to know of you,
[04:59.45]	Of whence you are, your name and parentage.
[05:03.38]PERICLES	A gentleman of Tyre; my name, Pericles;
